<html ><head ><meta charset="UTF-8"  /><meta name="author" content="Martin Walther - @tinuwalther"  /><meta name="keywords" content="Pode, PSHTML, PowerShell, Mermaid Diagram"  /><meta name="description" content="Builds beatuifull HTML-Files with PSHTML from native PowerShell-Scripts"  /><link href="/assets/BootStrap/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"  /><link href="/assets/style/style.css" rel="stylesheet"  /><script src="/assets/BootStrap/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"  ></script><title >#PSXi Help</title><link rel="icon" href="/assets/img/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon"  /></head><Body ><header ><div Class="jumbotron text-center" Id="j1" Style="padding:15; background-color:#033b63"  ><p ><h1 >#PSXi Help</h1></p><p >I ♥ PS Pode > This is an example for using pode and PSHTML, requested by API</p></div></header><Section Id="section"  ><nav Class="navbar navbar-expand-sm bg-dark navbar-dark sticky-top"  ><div Class="container-fluid"  ><a Target="_self" Class="navbar-brand" href="/"  >»HOME</a><button Class="navbar-toggler" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapsibleNavbar" type="button"  ><span Class="navbar-toggler-icon"  ></span></button><div Class="collapse navbar-collapse" Id="collapsibleNavbar"  ><ul Class="navbar-nav"  ><li Class="nav-item"  ><a Target="_self" Class="nav-link" href="#RebuildByFW"  >Re-build by FileWatcher</a></li><li Class="nav-item"  ><a Target="_self" Class="nav-link" href="#RebuildByAPI"  >Re-build by API</a></li></ul></div></div></nav><div Class="Container" Id="Content"  ><article Id="Pode"  ><h1 Style="color:#212529"  >Re-build pages</h1><p Style="color:#000"  >There are two methods to re-build all the pages.</p><h2 Id="RebuildByFW" Style="color:#212529"  >Re-build by FileWatcher</h2><p Style="color:#000"  >Re-builds the Index.pode page:</p><pre Style="color:#000"  >New-Item ./PodePSHTML/upload -Force -Name index.txt</pre><p Style="color:#000"  >Re-builds the Pode-Server.pode page:</p><pre Style="color:#000"  >NeNew-Item ./PodePSHTML/upload -Force -Name pode.txt</pre><p Style="color:#000"  >Re-builds the Update-Assets.pode page:</p><pre Style="color:#000"  >New-Item New-Item ./PodePSHTML/upload -Force -Name asset.txt</pre><p Style="color:#000"  >Re-builds the SQLite-Data.pode page:</p><pre Style="color:#000"  ><p Style="color:#000"  >`$SqlQuery = 'SELECT * FROM "classic_ESXiHosts" Limit 7'</p><p Style="color:#000"  >`$SqlQuery | Set-Content -Force -Path ./PodePSHTML/upload/sqlite.txt</p></pre><p Style="color:#000"  >Re-builds the Pester-Result.pode page:</p><pre Style="color:#000"  >New-Item ./PodePSHTML/upload -Force -Name pester.txt</pre><p Style="color:#000"  >Re-builds the Mermaid-Diagram.pode page:</p><pre Style="color:#000"  >New-Item ./PodePSHTML/upload -Force -Name mermaid.txt</pre><h2 Id="RebuildByAPI" Style="color:#212529"  >Re-build by API</h2><p Style="color:#000"  >Re-builds the Index.pode page:</p><pre Style="color:#000"  >Invoke-WebRequest -Uri http://localhost:8080/api/index -Method Post</pre><p Style="color:#000"  >Re-builds the Pode-Server.pode page:</p><pre Style="color:#000"  >Invoke-WebRequest -Uri http://localhost:8080/api/pode -Method Post</pre><p Style="color:#000"  >Re-builds the Update-Assets.pode page:</p><pre Style="color:#000"  >Invoke-WebRequest -Uri http://localhost:8080/api/asset -Method Post</pre><p Style="color:#000"  >Re-builds the SQLite-Data.pode page:</p><pre ><p Style="color:#000"  >`$SqlQuery = 'SELECT * FROM "classic_ESXiHosts" Limit 7'</p><p Style="color:#000"  >Invoke-WebRequest -Uri http://localhost:8080/api/sqlite -Method Post -Body `$SqlQuery</p></pre><p Style="color:#000"  >Re-builds the Pester-Result.pode page:</p><pre Style="color:#000"  >Invoke-WebRequest -Uri http://localhost:8080/api/pester -Method Post</pre><p Style="color:#000"  >Re-builds the Mermaid-Diagram.pode page:</p><pre Style="color:#000"  >Invoke-WebRequest -Uri http://localhost:8080/api/mermaid -Method Post</pre><p Style="color:#000"  >Re-builds the Help.pode page:</p><pre Style="color:#000"  >Invoke-WebRequest -Uri http://localhost:8080/api/help -Method Post</pre></article></div></Section></Body><div Class="container-fluid" Style="background-color:#343a40"  ><footer ><div Class="container-fluid"  ><div Class="row align-items-center"  ><div Class="col-md"  ><p ><a Target="_self" Class="btn-sm btn btn-outline-success" href="#"  >I ♥ PS ></a></p></div><div Class="col-md"  ><p >Based on <a Target="_blank" href="https://www.powershellgallery.com/packages/Pode"  >pode</a> and <a Target="_blank" href="https://www.powershellgallery.com/packages/PSHTML"  >PSHTML</a></p></div><div Class="col-md" Style="color:#000"  ><p >Created at 2024-07-16 21:19:30</p></div></div></div></footer></div></html>
